OL,5, Strikes by Border Force staff at UK    
OL,6, airports could go on for months unless 
OL,7, the government enters talks over pay,  
OL,8, the head of the PCS union has said.    
OL,10,FMark Serwotka said the union had a     
OL,11,F"mandate" for walkouts up until May.   
OL,13,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak said he was 
OL,14,F"sad" about disruption caused by       
OL,15,Fstrikes, but said he had acted "fairly 
OL,16,Fand reasonably" over public sector pay.
OL,18,FThousands of travellers arriving in the
OL,19,FUK had been told to expect delays but  
OL,20,Fso far disruption has been minimal.    
